data.description: Come see this super cute, updated 2 bed 2 bath cottage with a view!  Nestled in the hills of Terrebonne, close to town on a large lot with fencing.  Updated kitchen, new appliances, new carpet, new laminate flooring.  Updated bathrooms, new paint.  New roof 2023, new electrical.  364 sq ft 1 bed, 1 bath out building with Kitchenette and 35x24 shop behind the home.  Shed next to home 12x16.  Fenced front yard separate from fenced backyard.  Newer pellet stove, tons of great character all around.  The peaceful views are amazing!
